spi: Broadcom BRCMSTB, NSP, NS2 SoC bindings

Added device tree bindings documentation for BRCMSTB, NSP, NS2 iProc
SoCs supported by spi-bcm-qspi, spi-brcmstb-qspi and spi-iproc-qspi driver.

